DESCRIPTION:Recipe: Instant Pot Beef Stew Recipe\n(Leftover - no cooking needed!)\nServings: 6\nPrep: 15 min | Cook: 60 min | Total: 75 min\n\nTip: 🥛 DAIRY-FREE SWAPS: butter → vegan butter (Earth Balance). This Instant Pot Beef Stew recipe is incredibly fast and easy, but is packed with slow-cooked flavor. Perfect for those busy weeknights!\n\nSource: https://www.budgetbytes.com/instant-pot-beef-stew/
